snippet.title: Trove Closed Beta Trailer
snippet.description:
Trove Closed Beta has arrived! Play today in the voxel MMO set in a massive universe of online worlds. Adventure, explore, and create while hunting treasure in far-off lands – or building realms of your own!

Your adventure begins with one click. Sign up now. We can't wait to see what you'll create!

Play today – http://www.trovegame.com

Learn more at http://www.trionworlds.com/trove/ 

Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/TroveGame 
Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/TroveGame
